window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jace and his crew have broken through the Tempest Wall to find the world hidden within the hurricane.</b></p> <p>Now, they must head below to find the relic stolen from the Queen of Dragons.</p> <p>Their enemies from Saltwater's Weep have not forgotten them and remain hot on their heels, seeking to kill the adventurers as they grow in power. Old enemies are returning for a second chance at revenge and new enemies wait for their chance at a growing power.</p> <p>See Jace and his companions dominate the world beneath the waves as they fulfill their quests, gain power and advance far beyond the ability of their enemies to stop them.</p> <p><i>This story contains unusual relationships, explicit violence and content and a path to divinity.</i></p>"; 
